031200 1000-INITIALIZATION.                                             02750000
031300                                                                  02760000
031400     OPEN INPUT  DATE-FILE.                                       02770001
031500     OPEN OUTPUT MISSING-TRANS-FILE.                              02780001
031600                                                                  02790000
